pullRequest.title: Otp2 configure raptor search
pullRequest.bodyText:
Support for tuning transit/raptor using the router-config.json
- Change 'minTripTimeCoefficient' (DynamicSearchWindow) from float to double.
- Wrap config in a type, avoid passing JsonNode around. Enable using typed config classes, this allow reuse of config in e.g. the SpeedTest.
- Add Kryo Serializers for RouterConfigParams and GraphBuildParameters config classes.
- Use JsonNode toString instead of internal ReflectionLibrary to print config.
- Print correct source for config parameters when logging and throwing exceptions.
- Pushed Config parsing from the Router class to RouterConfigParams.
To be completed by pull request submitter:

 issue: No issue is added for this.
 roadmap: Raptor is on the roadmap.
 tests: UnitTests are added and updated.
 formatting: Yes
 documentation: The new config parameters are well documented in code, but need to be documented in the main documentation.
 changelog: This is part of implementing Raptor - changelog updated earlier.

To be completed by @opentripplanner/plc:

 reviews and approvals by 2 members, ideally from different organizations
 after merging: update the relevant card on the roadmap

commit.message: Code cleanup - Add a reusable JSON node adapter to support type-safe reading of JSON config. This enforce consistent error handling when reading config and logic reuse.

Support for tuning transit/raptor using the 'router-config.json'
- Change 'minTripTimeCoefficient' (DynamicSearchWindow) from float to double.
- Wrap config in a type, avoid passing JsonNode around. Enable using typed config classes, this allow reuse of config in e.g. the SpeedTest.
- Add Kryo Serializers for RouterConfigParams and GraphBuildParameters config classes.
- Use JsonNode toString instead of internal ReflectionLibrary to print config.
- Print correct source for config parameters when logging and throwing exceptions.
- Pushed Config parsing from the Router class to RouterConfigParams.

Clean code - Change performance logging to give better reports, add logging on "Transit data preparation" and "Street access/egress search", remove logging on "Raptor setup" takes 0 ms and "route by minute" witch is redundant.
Cleanup dynamic search window coefficients implementation with better naming and JavaDoc. A new unit test on search-window calculation is added.

beforeCommit.message: Cleanup dynamic search window coefficients implementation with better naming and JavaDoc. A new unit test on search-window calculation is added.

afterCommit.message:
Refactor and improve the configuration loading.
  - Reduce the DynamicSearchWindowCoefficients defaults even more.
  - Load config on startup and fail early on configuration errors.
  - Log warnings for all unused parameters, this is done by the NodeAdapter.
  - Log LOADED parameters for ALL config files.
  - Add more unit-tests on NodeAdapter.
  - Router config is changed:
    - The "routingDefaults" is explicit mapped into the default instance - at startup.
    - The two "timeout(s)" parameters is replaced by one single parameter: "streetRoutingTimeout".
    - The ReflectiveInitializer is deleted, the new NodeAdapter replaces this class.

nodes.bodyText: Add comment to say this only exists to construct an "immutable" instance with the right constructor. There might be a better way, a comment will help with any future refactor.
Add comment like the other serializer.
We have a merge conflict because other code does not yet use this constructor.
Generally use dots for nesting in JSON since those are used in the JSON itself.

commit.message:
Code review. Rename all config POJOs so the names are consistent and matches the configuration input JSON files. E.g. the 'BuildConfig' is the POJO for the 'build-config.json' file.
 - JavaDoc added to BuildConfigSerializer and RouterConfigSerializer.
 - '/' is replaced with '.' in config paths.
